HEADWORD: Calculator
<hw>Cal"cu*la*tor</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[L.: cf. F.
<ets>calculateur</ets>.]</ety> <def>One who computes or reckons: one who
estimates or considers the force and effect of causes, with a view to
form a correct estimate of the effects.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>Ambition is no exact <qex>calculator</qex>.</q>
<rj><qau>Burke.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Calculatory</ent>⟦br⟧
